{
  "stem": "24397.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So once we got into Holland, everybody gave a big cheer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I somehow looked upon it as sort of a big adventure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know what I really thought.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- somehow, I felt that once I get to England, like, I'm going to do things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm going to be able to bring them over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I guess a kid's illusions are such that they feel they can do anything and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think I had that feeling, the realization-- I didn't have the realization of what really was going on and certainly had no inkling that this was going to be a final good-bye.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived at Liverpool Street Station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] business associate of my father's was there to pick us up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took us to the Griggs' home in northwest London.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Griggs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] kind of introduced us and left us there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That, that was pretty much it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think we saw them again on one, on one occasion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "22nd of June, 1939.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we were enrolled in school immediately.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, we couldn't speak any English.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know a word of English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow, sign language seemed to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't even know how it came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the language came easily and quickly, especially when you have no, no alternative.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I think the age has a great deal to do with it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'd go to the school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they'd have composition.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she would tell me to write something in German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she would mark it A or-- [LAUGHS] she, she couldn't read it, either.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was, it was fine.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
